(264, 'Suleyman Abdirahman', 'Team Crank', 'I love the idea that you guys have, it will be very practical and something millions of people would use. I really like how you guys plan to use reusable material to build the product. I wish you guys submitted more within the logbook. It would of been nice to be able to see the sketches for the product. It also would of been nice to have more information about the circuit you guys want to use. The video quality was not the best and wish you guys worked on it. Overall the idea is amazing and I hope you guys continues to work on this product so i might buy it for my camping trips.'),
(265, 'Suleyman Abdirahman', 'Team Watta-Box', 'It is a great and Very practical idea, amazing job guys. This product is a very simple idea that solves a problem that we are all dealing with. The logbook was great, had all the information that I wanted to see. The only thing that I would of like to see was having the product floating in sometime of body of water. Overall amazing job, please continue working on this '),
