(319, 228, '<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Read any book in Braille</strong></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>&nbsp;Easy Braille reader/display</strong></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>&nbsp;Easy Braille Display</strong></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>&nbsp;Book to braille translator</strong></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n ', '<p><strong>Easy Braille book-reader</strong></p>\r\n ', '<p><strong>My invention helps the visually impaired read regular books that have not been printed in Braille. An additional function of my invention is that it can also be used by the visually impaired to read from electronic devices such as laptops or cell phones.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>My invention will make printed books easily accessible to the visually impaired and will have the following social benefits:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>More likely to complete high School and higher education</strong></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>More likely to seek and retain employment, economically independent</strong></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Improved quality of life</strong></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '2022-02-19 07:18:49'),
