(64, 319, 228, '<p>My invention is different from the others in the market in the following ways.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>No other product makes regular printed book accessible to the visually impaired.</strong></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Cost effective, sustainable&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Slim/small form factor.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Can use sustainable energy source&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>innovative soft pneumatic actuators.&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n ', '<p>My target audience is anyone who is visually impaired or blind regardless of age.</p>\r\n ', '<p><strong>Book 2 Braille decoder</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Easy Braille reader</strong></p>\r\n', '<p><strong>I like the name &rdquo;Book2Braille&rdquo; as it explains the function of my invention clearly.&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n', '2022-02-19 07:21:09'),
