(331, 229, ' ', '<p>I will get my parts at home appliance stores and if I cant find them there I will search for them online.&nbsp;</p>\r\n ', '<p>I will need to understand how water pumps work and how to set up a water system. I will also need to understand how hydraulic&nbsp;pumps work because half of the invention will be below the ground.&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>The people who can help me are my parents and my mentors. My mentors will help a lot since if I really need to I can use the labs at emu.&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2022-02-18 03:25:39'),
(332, 231, '<p>The materials that I will need are, plywood(8$), roof flashing (8$), copper tubing (20$), nuts and bolts (2$), mirror spray paint(11$), and duct tape (1$). some of the tools that I will need are a drill, a sander, and a table saw.</p>\r\n ', '<p>I got the copper tubing and roof flashing&nbsp;at Peter&#39;s true value hardware, and I got the plywood, duct tape, and the nuts and bolts, in my garage. Lastly I got the mirror spray paint on Amazon.com.</p>\r\n ', '<p>I will need to be able to sodar the copper tubing, cut the plywood, and drill the wholes in the plywood.</p>\r\n', '<p>My Dad helped me build the invention.</p>\r\n', '2022-02-18 04:30:19'),
