(331, 229, '<p>The part and materials I would need to make this would be very expensive for me to build so instead im making a prototype to demostrate what would happen at the cleaning phase. I used house tools and house materials. The materials I did use was water resistance tape(5$), two plastics boxes(15$), hotglue(5$), fish pump(25$). So my prototype would total to 50 dollares.&nbsp;</p>\r\n ', '<p>I will get all these materials from my house or home depot.&nbsp;</p>\r\n ', '<p>I will need to understand how water pumps work and how to set up a water system for my demo prototype. But if I was going to build my real prototype I would need to know how to work with metal, pressure washers, and hydraulic pumps.&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>The people who can help me are my parents and my mentors. My mentors will help a lot since if I need to I can use the labs at emu.&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2022-05-07 03:00:50'),
