(106, 369, 246, '<p>We could encounter malfunctions, the grease cleaner could start getting built up if people don&#39;t clean properly, leaving residue on the spatula&nbsp; causing cross contamination. Yes, this design is compatible with the principle of sustainability if it is properly taken care of. If it is properly taken care of it could last 3-4 years. I talked to my mom and showed her the design, she said</p>\r\n', '<p>If the machine malfunctions we would have a packet that comes with the flipper and at the back of it would be a checklist for common issues with the machine and if the person cannot figure out the problem thru the checklist there would be contact information at the bottom of the list for a technician,And the way we combat people not knowing how to take care of it is because In this very same packet there would be a introtructings on how to clean and take care of the machine this would tell you how often to clean the machine and how to do check-ups on the it to make sure everything is in perfect condition.&nbsp;</p>\r\n ', '<p>We made a few different designs before deciding on one specific design. Most of our designs did not implement as many movements but in our last design we chose to have 3 gears instead of the original 1-2 maximum amount of movement possible. Some more designs did not have the cleaner but we ended up going with a cleaner so that there&nbsp; will be no cross contamination.</p>\r\n', '2022-02-05 21:26:05'),
(107, 370, 248, '<p>the design might not work,problems with the software maybe?so i talked to my teammates about this design.</p>\r\n', '<p>we could restart our camera/software</p>\r\n ', '', '2022-02-05 21:46:33'),
