(109, 270, 230, '<p>We couldn&#39;t have a lid on our box because you couldn&#39;t seal the vacuum bag with a lid.&nbsp; We had to make a custom box because vacuum bags have nozzles in different spots.&nbsp; I talked to my mentor, Harinnere, about my design.&nbsp; She said that to think of the problems from different perspectives and the resources it would take to make the device.</p>\r\n', '<p>Use different vacuum bags that might fight better or a lid that more easily opens and closes without blocking the vacuum bag.</p>\r\n ', '', '2022-02-08 05:51:54'),
(110, 270, 230, '<p>We couldn&#39;t have a lid on our box because you couldn&#39;t seal the vacuum bag with a lid.&nbsp; We had to make a custom box because vacuum bags have nozzles in different spots.&nbsp; I talked to my mentor, Harinnere, about my design.&nbsp; She said that to think of the problems from different perspectives and the resources it would take to make the device.</p>\r\n', '<p>Use different vacuum bags that might fight better or a lid that more easily opens and closes without blocking the vacuum bag.</p>\r\n ', '', '2022-02-08 05:54:29'),
