(332, 231, '<p><strong>This is my problem: Solar energy is expensive because of its conversion process so not many people use it.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>This is how I came up with the problem: My mom and dad wanted to get solar panels for our house, but it was to expensive so we could not aford it so we did not get it.</strong></p>\r\n', '<p>What I want to achieve is a cheap and durable solar applience that people would want to buy.</p>\r\n', '<p>Here are some posible solutions:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. Figure a way to stop waste /leaks during conversion</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Make solar panels catch more energy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Do not convert energy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. Solar panels that are smaller but can get twice as much energy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. Make cheaper solar panels</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6. Make light/ bulbs that will use less energy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7. Make environment less energy consuming.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>8. <strong>Use DC appliances only-Have high powered house appliances consume DC instead of AC</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>I chose number 8,&nbsp;Use DC appliances only-Have high powered house appliances consume DC instead of AC. I cose this one because we were talking about the levels of which I could invent at.&nbsp;These are the levels; Household, Neiborhood, and world wide. I did not want to go to big so I chose the household level. So I thought well I could change one of our home appliances to change to Direct current (DC), and thats when I did some research and saw that stoves were one of the most&nbsp;energy consuming home&nbsp;appliances, so that is when the solar stoves came in.</p>\r\n', '2022-01-17 19:55:56'),
