(345, 235, '<p>Problem that we are trying to solve to avoid collision between two cars or&nbsp;obstacle that cause someone leads to dead or paralyzed .I came up with the problem &nbsp;by seeing many accident in the road . So thats why I decided to make a prototype which will help to avoid the accident .</p>\r\n', '<p>The result that we are trying to acheive by using something which has the ability to detect the&nbsp;obstacle and trying to stop before gonna hit&nbsp;the things.&nbsp;So wanna design a such&nbsp;kindof prototype whose detection power will save damages .&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Some possible solutions are :</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1) using backup cameras, 2) using utra sonic sensor that detect the obstacle</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3) voice command control / Bluethoot&nbsp; 4)Automatic emergency bracking&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I will go with the solution no 2 . Making a robot or machine whose gonna detect the obstacle&nbsp;by using ultra sonic sensor .&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2022-02-05 17:06:19'),
