(367, 246, '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; I am trying to solve the problem of food burning while it&#39;s cooking on the stove. For example, you are cooking a pancake and you have to walk away to let your dog in from outside. After you let your dog back in you see that your pancake is burnt and no longer edible. If you were to have a food flipper it would have prevented the pancake from burning. I came up with this problem by brainstorming problems that have occurred to me before.</p>\r\n', '<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; The result in trying to achieve this is that food no longer gets burnt and wasted while you&#39;re trying to focus on other important problems.</p>\r\n', '<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Some possible solutions are making an automatic food flipper or even making a food flip timer so that it goes off when your food of choice you&#39;re making needs to be flipped so that it does not get burnt. We chose to pursue the Food flipper, we decided to use this invention because it has many more benefits and it&#39;s a helpful tool. This tool is also used for people who are disbabled and can not flip food.</p>\r\n', '2022-02-05 21:23:50'),
(367, 248, '<p>The problem im trying to solve is racial discrimination in face regonition technology. Face recognition technology is racist, from how it was built to how it is used. It&rsquo;s been used by police departments to wrongfully arrest Black Americans. I came about this problem colored people are most likely to get arrested from crimes they didn&#39;t commit</p>\r\n', '<p>. The result im trying to achieve is making a model such as an upgraded and more effect camera that can clearly recognize each individual</p>\r\n', '<p>Facial recognition results highly rely on the quality of the image and the influence of factors such as lighting, occlusion, the person&#39;s pose, and race. One way to improve face recognition is to collect versatile training datasets with detailed visual data. I&#39;ve decided this because this is the only way to solve my problem</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2022-02-05 21:43:30'),
