(270, 230, '<p>I want to solve the problem of plastic bags getting into the ocean and harming sea life.&nbsp; Plastic bags can take up a lot of space to store before disposing and I wanted to find a way to keep the bags from getting loose and ending up in the ocean.</p>\r\n', '<p>I want to make it easy to store used plastic bags so they don&#39;t get loose and end up in the ocean.</p>\r\n', '<p>Make the bags biodegradable.&nbsp; I decided not to try this solution because it will take too long and are expensive to make.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ban plastic bags.&nbsp; I decided not to try this solution because then I would need to make stores have them put prices on the plastic bags.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trapping plastic bags at the source.&nbsp; I&nbsp;went with this one because it was the easiest&nbsp;to solve&nbsp;and&nbsp;could be used by anyone who wanted to keep plastic bags out of the ocean.</p>\r\n', '2022-02-08 05:44:52');
