(229, 'Smart Contamination Recycling Aid', 'The problem I am trying to fix is 34 percent of waste is recycled but 25 percent of the recyclables are contaminated. Which reduces the already low recycling rate of 34 percent to only 25.5 percent. The material which would be going to recycling is now instead going to the trash. ', '../test_upload/Log Book.pdf', NULL, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cIF4KM_t_mg', NULL, '6-8', '2022', 0),
